Package polyglot.ast

Class JLangToJLDel

java.lang.Object
polyglot.ast.JLang_c
polyglot.ast.JLangToJLDel
All Implemented Interfaces:
JLang, Lang
public class JLangToJLDel
extends JLang_c
JLangToDel_c is a bridge class that provides backward compatibility with the Polyglot's old architecture that uses delegate objects. It forwards operations to the node's delegate object.
